---
// src/components/Differentiators.astro
---

<section
  class="relative overflow-hidden bg-white/5 dark:bg-[#181818] px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 lg:py-32"
>
  <!-- Radial overlay adds subtle contrast in dark mode -->
  <div
    class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 hidden dark:block"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-radial from-transparent via-transparent to-black/40"
    >
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl text-center">
    <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold sm:text-4xl">
      What Makes Optimize Different
    </h2>

    <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <!-- Performance-first builds -->
      <div
        class="diff-card rounded-2xl bg-gray-50/90 dark:bg-[#1B1B1B]/60 p-8 shadow-lg ring-1 ring-slate-200/60 dark:ring-[#2A2A2A] transition transform hover:scale-[1.03] text-left"
      >
        <div
          class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent-primary/20 text-accent-primary mb-4"
        >
          <!-- icon unchanged -->
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="h-6 w-6"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke="currentColor"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold">
          Performance-Focused Websites
        </h3>
        <div class="mt-1 h-1 w-12 bg-accent-primary rounded"></div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-base text-muted-text">
          Every site is built with speed, accessibility, and usability in mind.
          Pages load quickly, layouts stay responsive, and performance best
          practices support both user experience and search visibility.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Clear pricing -->
      <div
        class="diff-card rounded-2xl bg-gray-50/90 dark:bg-[#1B1B1B]/60 p-8 shadow-lg ring-1 ring-slate-200/60 dark:ring-[#2A2A2A] transition transform hover:scale-[1.03] text-left"
      >
        <div
          class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent-secondary/20 text-accent-secondary mb-4"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="h-6 w-6"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke="currentColor"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v.01M12 6v-1h4l-1 1h-3Z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold">
          Clear, Predictable Pricing
        </h3>
        <div class="mt-1 h-1 w-12 bg-accent-secondary rounded"></div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-base text-muted-text">
          Straightforward scopes and fixed project pricing—no retainers, no
          surprise invoices, and no long-term lock-ins. You know exactly what
          you’re getting before work begins.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Direct builder access -->
      <div
        class="diff-card rounded-2xl bg-gray-50/90 dark:bg-[#1B1B1B]/60 p-8 shadow-lg ring-1 ring-slate-200/60 dark:ring-[#2A2A2A] transition transform hover:scale-[1.03] text-left"
      >
        <div
          class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent-primary/20 text-accent-primary mb-4"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="h-6 w-6"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke="currentColor"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 0 1-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8Z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold">
          Direct, Hands-On Collaboration
        </h3>
        <div class="mt-1 h-1 w-12 bg-accent-primary rounded"></div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-base text-muted-text">
          Work directly with the person building your site. Clear communication,
          regular updates, and responsive support ensure projects move
          efficiently and stay aligned with your goals.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
